706713f-a.folder: Sheepshead Bay Road & Jerome Avenue, Brooklyn, NY
706713f-a.original_title: Brooklyn: Sheepshead Bay Road - Jerome Avenue

706712f-b.text:
(1)
Sheepshead Bay Road, north side, west of Jerome Ave., sho ing from fore to background the home of C.F. O'Neil (1890), the Island View Hotel (1890) and another hotel having no name which still stands in 1937. The Island View was demolished prior to 1929, and the other frame structure
was modernized.
December 1923.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
(2)
The same, sho ing Nos. 1503-1523 Sheepshead Bay Road, beyond is the Brighton Beach Line of the B.M.T. This hotel,not named,is at the N.W.
corner of East 16th Street.
January 1924.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
